snippet.title: Across The Obelisk: Sands of Ulminin DLC Features Trailer
snippet.description:
Step through the portal to a new land of adventure. Sands of Ulminin is OUT NOW!

The Sands of Ulminin is a vast desert with untold secrets beneath its dunes. Adventure through a new zone in Acts 2 or 3 and recruit two new allies for your team, battle against unique new enemies, obtain new pets, and much more!

BUY NOW, on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2511580
